WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.222 --> 00:00:03.644
A couple of years ago
I only wore black,

00:00:03.640 --> 00:00:06.200
my inside also got black.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.911
But then when I found neon
I got very, very happy.

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:10.200
I like this color.

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:12.644
And started to dress 
colorful again.

00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:15.088
I got completely
obsessed with it,

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:16.777
started making 
my own neon pieces.

00:00:16.777 --> 00:00:19.800
How about here?
I've had a couple of electric shocks.

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.555
It makes me feel alive.

00:00:23.550 --> 00:00:25.977
Neon lights really 
fascinates me because

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:29.222
they are more 
than just a still piece of art.

00:00:29.220 --> 00:00:33.288
They have this gas 
dancing inside the tubes.

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:37.022
When you put neon 
in a very dark environment

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:40.533
all of a sudden 
it's beautiful.

00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.844
It helps me see the world 
in a new light

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:46.200
and brings people closer.

